<br>
Our system is a DKP system that uses a full loss system instead of a cost per item.  This means that whoever has the most points wins the item, but they then are reset to 0, meaning that loot is spread around the guild a lot.  It means that as we progress, those who play about the same ammount progress at about the same rate.<br>
<br>
It works great because in places like time, we will have 20-30 full loss items in p1-p4(we are up to TZ/VZ atm) and that causes major turn over in the points leaders.<br>
<br>
